Stage 2:Bargaining

There are pleas to others to see it as the true believers do. Expected profits are cited, and proof of delivered promises widely shared

But there's a flaw : a trade that initially worked due to sentiment does not suddenly turn into one with solid fundamentals

Those who cannot admit they have been duped will find only the virtues and ignore all the faults. 

Surely the stock will rebound, and true believers will buy into it.

 The stock falls.
